OL,3,CBarry Manilow laughs off stage invader
OL,4,Cat concert in Liverpool
OL,6,FSecurity officer removes a man from
OL,7,Fthe stage as crowd clap.
OL,9,FBarry Manilow laughed off a stage
OL,10,Finvader at his concert in Liverpool
OL,11,Fjoking "I'm irresistible".
OL,13,FThe performance was interrupted when
OL,14,Fthe man ran onto the stage at the M
OL,15,Fand S Bank Arena on Saturday June 13
OL,16,Fappearing to want an autograph.
OL,18,FA security officer bundled him off
OL,19,Fstage watched by the 11,000 strong
OL,20,Faudience.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
