OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781531287
OL,3,CBarry Manilow laughs off stage invader
OL,4,Cat concert in Liverpool
OL,6,FThe musician, who appeared unbothered
OL,7,Fby the incident, said: "Throw him out
OL,8,F- I'm just kidding".
OL,10,FManilow, 82, who was diagnosed with
OL,11,Flung cancer in December last year, has
OL,12,Fachieved seven UK top 10 albums,
OL,13,Fincluding a number one with Barry Live
OL,14,FIn Britain, and one UK top 10 single
OL,15,Fwith I Wanna Do It With You.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
