OL,3,CBarry Manilow laughs off stage invader
OL,4,Cat concert in Liverpool
OL,6,FHe began his career in the early
OL,7,F1960s, and had his first hit in the UK
OL,8,Fwith Mandy in 1975, and has gone on to
OL,9,Fsell more than 85 million records as a
OL,10,Fsolo artist worldwide, being nominated
OL,11,Ffor 15 Grammy Awards, and winning one.
